Sniper/Rhinox

Sniper waas getting board, There was nothing for him to do. He was 
checking the scanners watching to see if there would be an attack. 
None was coming, just alot of people leaving the base. From what He 
saw they weren't going far but ofcorse He didn't know of cared. If 
there was an attack He could Defend the Base. He just watch the 
scanners.


Rhinox looked at the outer hull of the Ark. It could hold. Rhinox 
started working on autoguns. He wanted the atleast a good job done on 
all of this.
